These are Puzzles for 1x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-1::.
2 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, pony
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the pony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |    2    |
| Pet   | guinea-pig | pony |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: coffee, iced-tea
1. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |   2    |
| Beverage   | coffee | iced-tea |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x2-Level-1-3::.
House: craftsman, art-deco
1. the craftsman house is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1  |   2   |
| House   | art-deco | craftsman |

 #################################

 
